title: Cooking in outer space
description: Finally! A course that will help you to make some pasta while you are traveling in outer space.

title: Doing dishes in outer space
description: It might be quite troublesome to clean your plate when there's basically nothing to breath. This course will help you to become a confident cleaner and prepare you for the next space odyssey.

title: Coding in outer space
description: Ever wondered how to code when you're in 0 gravity? Sure you didn't but we have this course for you anyway.

title: Not dying in outer space
description: This is by far the most important course among all the courses about doing stuff in outer space. Cause, you know, it's too easy to die when there's all that cosmic things you have no idea about around you.
